===============================================================================
  ABOUT
===============================================================================

Triality is a computational substrate for physically grounded reasoning. It
provides a programmable environment in which physics-aware models can analyze,
evaluate, and reason about systems that obey the laws of the physical
world. Triality operates as a core module within the Mentis OS ecosystem — a
broader initiative by Genovation to build intelligent systems that understand
reality at a fundamental level.

